column5: I've been to lac seul before, had great fishing. We went 2 weeks later any help with the lures I can start stocking up on. Gonna be fishing walleye's mainly, but jack fishing is just too much fun. Fishing and hunting are the only sports for a 15yr old.
We also have plans for June 21-28 at Whitewing Resort. See you there.
